reviewText: More fun with your friendly guppies on a farm lifestyle and beyond.

This movie is so cute my little girl loves this movie. She watches it over and over she gets up and dances and sings with them It is the cutest thing. I highly recommend this movie.

My sweet baby boy loves Bubble Guppies. I love them because they have the sweetest characters and they teach our children so much. There are a lot of things out there to be wary of but these sweet cartoons are NOT it. Great character values taught and I love the graphics.

This DVD features five Bubble Guppies episodes. You can watch one at a time or two hours worth. It is a fun DVD with adventures of those silly mer-people. The show features great lessons and my kids love watching them. These episodes have previously aired on television but it is great to have them all on one DVD. Each of the episodes also feature animals which is perfect for animal lovers!

I received this product to review in exchange for sharing my honest opinion.

THERE ARE EPISODES IN THIS DVD:
BUBBLE GUPPIES EPISODE 11: HAVE A COW!,
BUBBLE GUPPIES EPISODE 13: THE SPRING CHICKEN IS COMING!
FROM NICKELODEON FAVORITES: SPRINGTIME ADVENTURES,
BUBBLE GUPPIES EPISODE 27: THE COWGIRL PARADE!
FROM NICKELODEON FAVORITES: ROOTIN' TOOTIN' WILD WEST,
BUBBLE GUPPIES EPISODE 57: THE BUBBLE BEE-ATHALON!
AND
BUBBLE GUPPIES EPISODE 62: BUBBLE KITTY!
FROM NICKELODEON FAVORITES: WHISKERS & PAWS

I bought this to get a few more episodes then what is free with Prime. I must say, I think it's my favorite toddler/young kids show out there. Teaches them a lot and isn't obnoxious. Some singing and dancing in each show, which my son (16months) is a huge fan of.
Great videos for my 2 year old! This dvd has I think 4 or 5 episodes of Bubble Guppies. ... last a good deal of time when we are traveling. Catchy tunes also! Fun for all!

I have a stash of "You did super good at the doctor today" for my toddler and this is what she picked out after her last appointment. The DVD arrived in perfect condition, the show itself is very good. Four stars because after watching it for the 100th time I want to rip my hair out.
